  "description": "Give me anonymous feedback.",
  "body_html": "<p>How am I holding myself back? </p><p>You can leave a <a href=\"https://www.admonymous.co/afiq-hatta\">note here</a>. Do your worst!</p><p>You can leave a note regardless of whether you know me personally, whether we\u2019ve chatted online, or however much you\u2019ve read any of my stuff. </p><p>It doesn\u2019t have to be about just my writing. It could be on my views, process, how I\u2019ve spoken to you, whether I\u2019ve helped, my writing style, experiments or otherwise. Kind words are appreciated, but I\u2019m mainly looking for constructive criticism .</p><p>Thank you. </p><p></p>",
  "truncated_body_text": "How am I holding myself back?",
